## Phase 3 — Service Layer

Created 3 domain services to eliminate duplicated business logic:

### [bookingService.js](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/services/bookingService.js)

| Function | Replaces | Call Sites |
|----------|----------|------------|
| [syncRoomAvailability()](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/services/bookingService.js#89-150) | ~30-line room increment/decrement/cap/sync block | 3 (admin, owner, student leave) |
| [coerceMealsSelected()](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/services/bookingService.js#5-30) | ~15-line boolean coercion block | 2 (create, leave) |
| [meetsBookingVerification()](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/services/bookingService.js#68-88) | ~10-line inline verification check | 1 (create) |
| [isVerificationFresh()](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/routes/bookingRoutes.js#13-25) / [isAadhaarFresh()](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/controllers/bookingController.js#27-38) | Local helpers | Shared utility |

### [reviewService.js](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/services/reviewService.js)

| Function | Replaces | Call Sites |
|----------|----------|------------|
| [getReviewsWithDistribution()](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/services/reviewService.js#19-74) | ~30-line sort + query + aggregation pipeline | 2 (property, mess) |
| [buildSortObject()](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/services/reviewService.js#4-18) | Duplicate switch statement | Internal |

### [verificationService.js](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/services/verificationService.js)

| Function | Replaces | Call Sites |
|----------|----------|------------|
| [updateVerificationState()](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/services/verificationService.js#27-72) | ~30-line inline state transition logic | 1 (adminVerify) |
| [markVerificationFailed()](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/services/verificationService.js#73-91) | Inline user state update | 1 (expired doc) |
| [getDocumentCategory()](file:///c:/Users/mukun/Downloads/staysafe/Backend/src/services/verificationService.js#3-26) | Local helper function | 1 (upload) |

