## Verification

All refactored endpoints verified after Phase 3:

| Endpoint | Status | Meaning |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `GET /api/mess` | 200 | Public endpoint ✅ |
| `GET /api/bookings` | 401 | Auth + booking service ✅ |
| `GET /api/reviews/property/:id` | OK | Review service ✅ |
| `GET /api/documents/my-documents` | 401 | Auth + verification service ✅ |

## Architecture After Phase 3

```mermaid
graph TD
  subgraph Routes
    R["Route Files<br/>(thin routing)"]
  end
  subgraph Controllers
    C["Controllers<br/>(request/response)"]
  end
  subgraph Services
    BS["bookingService"]
    RS["reviewService"]
    VS["verificationService"]
    NS["notificationService"]
    ES["emailService"]
  end
  subgraph Data
    M["Models"]
  end
  R --> C
  C --> BS & RS & VS & NS
  BS & RS & VS --> M
  NS --> ES
```
